Orco Property Says Restructuring May Be Through Bond Conversion

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-10-07T13:34:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/orco-property-says-restructuring-may-be-through-bond-conversion.html
Orco Property Group (ORCO)  SA is in talks
with bondholders about debt restructuring that may take the form
of a bond conversion, the Czech developer said today on its
 website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
